'''Hobgoblins''' are [[monster]]s that are commonly killed for [[limpwurt root]]s. They can be found on a peninsula behind the [[Crafting Guild]], in the [[Edgeville Dungeon]] (bring a [[brass key]] for easier access) in the [[Wilderness]] [[Wilderness hobgoblin mine|Hobgoblin mine]], in [[Witchaven dungeon]], [[Gnome Village Dungeon]] and inside [[Strange Barrel]]s.

